    "the associated output layer and all the layers below.",
    "EvaluationTo be consistent with previous results and due to nondeterminism in deep neural networks [67], we repeated the experiments and averaged the results.",
    "According to Cohan et al. [17], we performed three random restarts for PMD and NIC and used the same train/validation/test sets.",
    "For DRI and ART, we performed tenfold and ninefold cross-validation, respectively, as in the original papers [29,52].",
    "Within each fold, the data is split into train/validation/test sets with the proportions k-2 k / 1 k / 1 k where k is the number of folds."
